dc_description_s: This polygon shapefile represents countour lines of Mendocino County in California. This is a reprojected version of a countour layer of Mendocino County originally created by the North Coast Regional Water Quality Control Board.This layer can be used for watershed analysis and planning in the Russian River region of California.
